We recommend that the Municipal Mayor:

1. Require the Municipal Accountant to submit immediately the financial statements and supporting schedules as of December 31, 2013;

2.  Require the Municipal Accountant and Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Budget Officer to strictly adhere to the provisions of Section 2.1.1-2.19 of COA Circular No. 2010-001.

We strongly recommend that Management undertake the following:

Refrain from resorting to procurement and disbursements through reimbursement procedure. All payments should pass through the regular mode of procurement and disbursement procedures in accordance with the provisions of RA 9184;

Comply with the requirement of adequate procurement planning in accordance with Section 7 of RA 9184;

Submit explanation for purchases made through reimbursement and the lack of adequate supporting documents as mentioned above. Otherwise, the same shall be disallowed in audit; and

Require that all disbursements or claims against the LGU be supported with complete documents.
